name: The New Variant
description: these two years we have been made nervous by the news and crazy ideas of a group of people, the various ways they create issues and news that make us restless, life is not calm, 2020 is a year full of hope, many goals and dreams that we have planned, in the end we have to postpone and may fail it, from year to year every human being grows with new aspirations and hopes, but what can they do to make similar issues and news in continuous upgrades, with new names, new variants, born every year, I believe the disease exists, but always There are conspiracies and parties who benefit from this news and ideas.
